    "Project Description:",
    null,
    null,
    "This project is located on Highway PR-176 from kilometer 0.00 to 4.00 for total length of 4 km. The Pavement Rehabiltation and Safety Improvement Project for PR-176, commences at its intersection with PR-1 and continue along the exixting highway up to the intersection with PR-199 in the municipality of San Juan. The proposed works consist of the improvements to the exixting roadside safety elements at highway PR-176. The works to be performed also include: maintenance and protection of traffic, cold milling and placement of bituminous pavement, the aplication thermoplastic pavement marking, installation of traffic signs, removal, storage and delivered of exixting guard rail, furnishing and installation of Wbeam guard rail single face and double face, contruction of new transition  modules traffic signals and other miscellaneous works as shown on plans."
